WEBVTT

00:00:47.392 --> 00:00:49.215
Pass me the ball, hurry up!

00:00:49.215 --> 00:00:51.451
Quick, pass the ball, hurry!

00:00:52.256 --> 00:00:53.286
Pass me the ball!

00:00:53.286 --> 00:00:54.788
Here!

00:00:54.788 --> 00:00:56.022
Hollow layup scores.

00:01:08.468 --> 00:01:09.636
Sorry.

00:01:11.971 --> 00:01:13.760
I'm so sorry. Which department are you from?

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:15.442
Let's go.

00:01:15.442 --> 00:01:16.512
Sorry.

00:01:17.077 --> 00:01:18.112
Sorry about that.

00:01:22.649 --> 00:01:23.750
Some people say

00:01:23.750 --> 00:01:26.352
love is like an apple hanging on a tree,

00:01:27.454 --> 00:01:29.289
always unsteady.

00:01:30.623 --> 00:01:32.325
So if gravity brings

00:01:32.325 --> 00:01:35.228
Newton and the apple together,

00:01:37.630 --> 00:01:39.365
we should study it carefully,

00:01:40.433 --> 00:01:43.536
or just take a bite and eat it.

00:01:45.271 --> 00:01:46.506
Are you immune enough?

00:01:47.273 --> 00:01:48.708
Pretend to be fearless.

00:01:48.708 --> 00:01:49.709
Going forward, go, go, go.

00:01:50.810 --> 00:01:53.530
Unfortunately, you're hit by a dart.

00:01:53.530 --> 00:01:56.816
You still need to find a way
to get the antidote.

00:01:57.617 --> 00:01:59.119
If you want the antidote,

00:02:00.086 --> 00:02:04.190
better to rely on yourself and charge forward.

00:02:04.190 --> 00:02:06.292
If you're lucky enough to be hit by the dart,

00:02:06.292 --> 00:02:09.796
treat it as an experience
to strengthen your immunity.

00:02:15.398 --> 00:02:21.312
[Newton and the Apple]

00:02:21.888 --> 00:02:24.608
♫ When I think of you ♫

00:02:24.608 --> 00:02:30.208
♫ I think about the first time we met ♫

00:02:30.208 --> 00:02:31.744
♫ Suddenly my heart flipped ♫

00:02:32.256 --> 00:02:37.824
♫ And I fall into the life of a drama play ♫

00:02:39.887 --> 00:02:43.648
♫ You're Newton, and I'm the apple ♫

00:02:43.648 --> 00:02:47.392
♫ Falling from the tree ♫

00:02:47.392 --> 00:02:49.984
♫ Oh, take a bite ♫

00:02:49.984 --> 00:02:54.624
♫ Just like fish needs water ♫

00:02:54.624 --> 00:02:58.368
♫ You're Summer, and I'm the breeze ♫

00:02:58.368 --> 00:03:03.392
♫ Blowing from the sea ♫

00:03:03.392 --> 00:03:09.792
♫ I don't understand why love always
makes people feel at a loss ♫

00:03:11.263 --> 00:03:14.304
[Stay by My Side]

00:03:39.648 --> 00:03:40.687
Watch this.

00:03:44.324 --> 00:03:45.525
Come on, split into two teams.

00:03:45.525 --> 00:03:46.526
Three on three.

00:03:50.863 --> 00:03:51.998
Hi, Junior.

00:03:51.998 --> 00:03:54.133
I heard you were good at basketball
in high school.

00:03:54.133 --> 00:03:55.935
Why don't you join the basketball team?

00:03:55.935 --> 00:03:57.170
Not interested.

00:03:57.170 --> 00:03:59.305
Jiang, I heard you transferred
from the medical school,

00:03:59.305 --> 00:04:00.740
making the dean very regretful.

00:04:00.740 --> 00:04:02.442
Your dad even called to check,

00:04:02.442 --> 00:04:04.510
thinking you might have been wronged.

00:04:06.512 --> 00:04:07.947
Since you're in law school now,

00:04:07.947 --> 00:04:10.016
we should invite your parents to dinner.

00:04:10.016 --> 00:04:11.684
No need. You're not familiar.

00:04:12.885 --> 00:04:15.054
You can study here with ease.

00:04:15.054 --> 00:04:17.690
All staff in the law school will do our best

00:04:17.690 --> 00:04:18.891
to make you satisfied.

00:04:18.891 --> 00:04:21.160
Come on, tell me if you have any needs.

00:04:25.999 --> 00:04:28.101
I want to apply for a dorm room.

00:04:29.836 --> 00:04:32.005
No problem. I'll arrange it right away.

00:04:33.706 --> 00:04:35.008
Be careful.

00:04:39.512 --> 00:04:40.580
Are you okay?

00:04:42.548 --> 00:04:44.550
Sorry about that.

00:04:52.925 --> 00:04:54.227
Who's this? Not bad.

00:04:54.227 --> 00:04:55.228
Pretty good.

00:04:55.828 --> 00:04:56.863
He's not bad.

00:05:05.905 --> 00:05:08.541
Senior said fate can only be encountered
but not sought.

00:05:08.541 --> 00:05:10.276
When the time comes, it will come,

00:05:10.276 --> 00:05:11.444
and you can't avoid it.

00:05:12.045 --> 00:05:13.813
Brother, come back for a visit.

00:05:13.813 --> 00:05:15.040
What for?

00:05:15.040 --> 00:05:18.217
Senior said he's officially
handing over the temple to me.

00:05:18.217 --> 00:05:20.753
I'm having a small party to celebrate.

00:05:21.754 --> 00:05:23.656
I might not have time.

00:05:23.656 --> 00:05:25.058
That's a pity.

00:05:25.058 --> 00:05:27.226
Senior said he wanted to strengthen your seal

00:05:27.226 --> 00:05:29.062
before setting off on his trip.

00:05:29.062 --> 00:05:31.064
Sister, I'll book a train ticket right away.

00:05:31.064 --> 00:05:32.632
You must ask Senior to wait for me.

00:05:32.632 --> 00:05:33.633
You're so heartless.

00:05:33.633 --> 00:05:35.501
You still know I'm your sister.

00:05:36.135 --> 00:05:38.604
But Senior helped me with everything
when I was growing up.

00:05:38.604 --> 00:05:40.573
And you hit me and took my stuff.

00:05:52.485 --> 00:05:53.953
In life, we will always face certain things

00:05:53.953 --> 00:05:56.756
that we don't want but must defend.

00:05:56.756 --> 00:05:57.990
For example…

00:07:08.494 --> 00:07:09.629
Damn it!

00:07:10.830 --> 00:07:12.064
Who are you?

00:07:12.064 --> 00:07:13.399
Why are you in my room?

00:07:16.669 --> 00:07:17.837
What are you doing here…

00:07:18.638 --> 00:07:19.939
Starting today,

00:07:19.939 --> 00:07:21.607
half of this room is mine.

00:07:24.377 --> 00:07:26.813
Are you sure you want to stay in this room?

00:07:26.813 --> 00:07:28.581
This place is haunted.

00:07:39.008 --> 00:07:40.059
It's you…

00:07:40.059 --> 00:07:41.394
Jiang Chi.

00:07:41.394 --> 00:07:42.628
You are the ghost.

00:07:43.863 --> 00:07:45.531
Why are you so rude?

00:07:57.143 --> 00:07:58.644
What's wrong with you?

00:07:58.644 --> 00:08:00.146
Why are you messing with my stuff?

00:08:00.146 --> 00:08:01.781
Starting today, this is my room too.

00:08:03.616 --> 00:08:05.718
Are you sure you want to live here?

00:08:05.718 --> 00:08:07.353
This place is really haunted.

00:08:07.954 --> 00:08:10.223
Look at this bed and that bed.

00:08:10.223 --> 00:08:12.792
No one lives here because of the haunting.

00:08:12.792 --> 00:08:15.061
The dorm supervisor said they're
occupying the beds while living off-campus,

00:08:15.061 --> 00:08:16.229
a bad example.

00:08:19.232 --> 00:08:21.767
Is there anything else
I should know that I don't?

00:08:23.336 --> 00:08:26.672
The dorm supervisor wouldn't dare
tell you this place is really haunted.

00:08:27.640 --> 00:08:29.208
Then why do you still dare to live here?

00:08:30.443 --> 00:08:33.145
I come from a temple, protected by gods.

00:08:33.980 --> 00:08:35.515
Check it out.

00:08:35.515 --> 00:08:36.883
Come, let me tell you.

00:08:37.517 --> 00:08:39.385
There was a student here.

00:08:39.385 --> 00:08:41.487
He used to be bullied all the time,

00:08:41.487 --> 00:08:44.357
and he could only hide in the dorm
and cry by himself.

00:08:44.357 --> 00:08:46.826
One day, he cried himself to sleep.

00:08:46.826 --> 00:08:47.994
And then,

00:08:48.594 --> 00:08:50.930
he was electrocuted and no one knew.

00:08:51.664 --> 00:08:53.799
He wasn't discovered until several days later.

00:08:54.567 --> 00:08:56.536
The resentment here is really heavy.

00:08:56.536 --> 00:08:58.404
Are you sure you want to live here?

00:08:59.038 --> 00:09:00.573
Hallucinations or environments

00:09:00.573 --> 00:09:02.775
can cause mental confusion and misperception.

00:09:03.309 --> 00:09:06.345
Thinking you've seen a ghost
is just because you're timid.

00:09:56.295 --> 00:09:57.930
Why were you so fierce today?

00:09:58.798 --> 00:09:59.966
I'm annoyed.

00:09:59.966 --> 00:10:02.301
Someone moved into my dorm room.

00:10:02.301 --> 00:10:05.171
He wears and uses high-end stuff,

00:10:05.171 --> 00:10:06.806
so why does he have to live with me

00:10:06.806 --> 00:10:08.991
in a dorm without any private space?

00:10:08.991 --> 00:10:10.977
Why pretend to be poor?

00:10:10.977 --> 00:10:12.345
What's there to be annoyed about?

00:10:12.345 --> 00:10:14.046
It's not like a ghost moved in.

00:10:14.046 --> 00:10:15.114
You guys don't understand.

00:10:15.114 --> 00:10:16.449
When I was young, my biggest hope

00:10:16.449 --> 00:10:18.117
was to have a room all to myself.

00:10:18.117 --> 00:10:20.853
Please, how long have you monopolized
the three-person room?

00:10:20.853 --> 00:10:22.021
Exactly.

00:10:22.021 --> 00:10:24.790
I even thought you might have asked your sister
to drive people away with magic.

00:10:27.760 --> 00:10:29.261
Good idea.

00:10:29.261 --> 00:10:30.830
I can ask my sister to cast a spell

00:10:30.830 --> 00:10:32.865
and drive away this rude person.

00:10:37.403 --> 00:10:38.771
Jiang Chi?

00:10:40.406 --> 00:10:41.941
Gu Buxia, where are you going?

00:10:41.941 --> 00:10:42.976
Practice isn't over yet.

00:10:42.976 --> 00:10:44.076
What is he doing?

00:10:44.076 --> 00:10:45.111
What's he doing?

00:10:45.111 --> 00:10:46.112
Is he going crazy?

00:10:46.112 --> 00:10:47.113
Yeah, he's been like that lately.

00:11:01.260 --> 00:11:03.429
Know yourself and know your enemy,
and you will win every battle.

00:12:06.392 --> 00:12:07.693
He says he has no money,

00:12:07.693 --> 00:12:09.962
yet he gives such an expensive helmet
to a girl.

00:13:00.780 --> 00:13:02.815
This guy actually uses a second-hand one.

00:13:06.152 --> 00:13:08.487
[Your order is about to be delivered]

00:13:12.158 --> 00:13:13.225
Why is it you?

00:13:13.225 --> 00:13:14.493
385.

00:13:15.427 --> 00:13:16.929
Your takeaway order takes cash.

00:13:16.929 --> 00:13:18.297
It's 385.

00:13:31.076 --> 00:13:32.545
Are you really short on money?

00:13:32.545 --> 00:13:35.080
Why did you change to such an ugly helmet?

00:13:41.153 --> 00:13:42.488
Do you want to drink bubble tea?

00:13:43.756 --> 00:13:45.424
Eating too much trans-fat will make you dumb.

00:13:45.925 --> 00:13:47.359
What do you mean?

00:13:47.359 --> 00:13:49.094
The literal meaning.

00:13:53.332 --> 00:13:55.167
This is how you repay my kindness?

00:14:08.736 --> 00:14:09.849
What are you guys doing?

00:14:09.849 --> 00:14:11.550
Isn't your roommate called Jiang Chi?

00:14:12.918 --> 00:14:14.944
People always say it takes a hundred years
to travel on the same boat…

00:14:14.944 --> 00:14:16.640
- And a thousand years to…
- Share the same pillow.

00:14:16.640 --> 00:14:17.728
Right.

00:14:17.728 --> 00:14:20.125
I'll think of a way to make him move out soon.

00:14:20.125 --> 00:14:22.661
The captain means that you and your roommate
are destined to be living together,

00:14:22.661 --> 00:14:24.530
so you should get along well with him.

00:14:24.530 --> 00:14:25.664
Right.

00:14:25.664 --> 00:14:27.333
What are you guys trying to do?

00:14:27.867 --> 00:14:29.201
Get him on the basketball team.

00:14:29.201 --> 00:14:30.436
Huh?

00:14:30.436 --> 00:14:33.539
You want me to bring
that annoying jerk into the team?

00:14:34.974 --> 00:14:36.976
Our senior has a wish before graduation,

00:14:36.976 --> 00:14:39.545
which is to win a few games
in the college cup this year.

00:14:39.545 --> 00:14:42.147
We can't go home empty-handed like last year.

00:14:42.147 --> 00:14:43.382
It's so embarrassing.

00:14:43.382 --> 00:14:45.818
No problem, just leave it to me.

00:14:45.818 --> 00:14:47.903
Our team isn't just relying on you.

00:14:47.903 --> 00:14:50.055
It would be great to find someone
who can keep up with you.

00:14:50.055 --> 00:14:51.056
The captain means

00:14:51.056 --> 00:14:53.292
Jiang Chi was a scoring guard
in his high school basketball team,

00:14:53.292 --> 00:14:54.693
and everyone called him a sharpshooter.

00:14:55.227 --> 00:14:57.429
No way. If he's in, I'm out.

00:14:57.429 --> 00:14:59.265
I don't want to see him everywhere,

00:14:59.265 --> 00:15:00.666
even when playing basketball.

00:15:00.666 --> 00:15:02.501
This isn't the show "Wishing to See You".

00:15:05.037 --> 00:15:06.105
Buxia.

00:15:23.040 --> 00:15:24.156
So annoying.

