00:17:07.328 --> 00:17:11.360
♫ I want you in every breath
and in every touching moment ♫

00:17:11.360 --> 00:17:16.256
♫ Let's hold hands and walk in strides ♫

00:17:16.256 --> 00:17:19.705
♫ My chest is broad for you ♫

00:17:19.705 --> 00:17:20.939
I'll go first.

00:17:37.888 --> 00:17:39.024
Give it to me.

00:17:39.024 --> 00:17:40.926
No, I got it first.

00:18:06.018 --> 00:18:07.119
It's all your fault.

00:18:07.119 --> 00:18:08.821
Why did you fight with me for it?

00:18:38.817 --> 00:18:40.285
Junior.

00:18:40.285 --> 00:18:42.321
One of you studies anthropology, the other law.

00:18:42.321 --> 00:18:43.722
Fate brought you together in the same dorm.

00:18:43.722 --> 00:18:45.257
Do you have to fight like this?

00:18:46.125 --> 00:18:47.326
Senior.

00:18:47.326 --> 00:18:49.895
He's the one picking fights, not me.

00:18:52.531 --> 00:18:53.966
You're not elementary school students.

00:18:53.966 --> 00:18:55.434
Can you act more maturely?

00:18:56.768 --> 00:18:59.505
One person's immaturity
makes it hard for the mature one.

00:19:00.072 --> 00:19:01.874
All talk, no action.

00:19:09.615 --> 00:19:10.749
How about this?

