If you're going to live with me,

00:22:29.792 --> 00:22:31.283
- You must eat this.
- I don't want to.

00:22:31.283 --> 00:22:32.416
My potato chips.

00:22:32.416 --> 00:22:34.436
Gu Buxia, get off of me.

00:22:34.436 --> 00:22:36.421
Shouldn't dorm mates
take good care of each other?

